headline: 3 Reasons ALGN is Risky and 1 Stock to Buy Instead
summary: Shareholders of Align Technology would probably like to forget the past six months even happened. The stock dropped 21.4% and now trades at $185.24. This may have investors wondering how to approach the situation.
